However, the issue we are facing is the 500 internal server error happening on tickets. For cause Code we use a static code for all tickets, and the resolution is dynamically filled. If missing, we do see the appropriate error code on our side as well indicating we have missed out a key field.

Subject: The Zimco Group: ITSM & ITAM - 20 Concurrent Cloud Subscription
Symptom:
Quote request for The Zimco Group for 20 concurrent ITSM & ITAM cloud Subscription licenses.

The Zimco Group is a producer of industrial and base minerals, producer and supplier of secondary zinc, lead, aluminium metal and alloys, related chemicals, engineering plastics and industrial foam products.
 
Trevor Naicker is the Head of IT at The Zimco Group and LeadX, which are the holding companies for 7 companies.
Zimco Group subsidiaries: Dutton Plastics, Zimco Associated Additives, Zimco Metals, G&W Mineral Resources and Sondor.
LeadX subsidiaries: Frys Metals and Castle Lead Works.
They were both acquired by AutoX recently, who are allowing them to make their own IT decisions.
